cs.LG, cs.CR, cs.AI, cs.DS, cs.SE 

This paper deals with machine learning models and their vulnerability to data poisoning attacks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) as the paper focuses on data poisoning attacks. The paper also involves abstract interpretation, which is a technique used in Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Data Structures (cs.DS). Finally, the paper presents a tool called Antidote, which involves software engineering (cs.SE).
